    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken meticulous care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
