    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2). This example features the highly sought-after 3.8L DFI flat-six, delivering 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with a documented service history highlighting proactive maintenance of the PASM dampers and a pristine undercarriage. The naturally aspirated induction note remains crisp, and the factory-spec limited-slip differential provides exceptional corner-exit traction. Finished in concours-level paint with zero track-use fatigue, this chassis represents the pinnacle of hydraulic steering feel and analog engagement.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
