    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable survivor, presenting in a state that can only be described as showroom-fresh. Every inch of the exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like clarity, free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, having been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Step inside to a cabin that still carries a subtle new-car scent; the high-grade leather upholstery is supple with absolutely no wear on the bolsters, and every piece of switchgear operates with a crisp, factory-tight feel. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented, open-checkbook service history with all fluids and filters recently refreshed. From the immaculate engine bay to the pristine undercarriage, this car is a definitive example for a discerning collector seeking a turn-key, flawless driving experience.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
