      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects meticulous care, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior. Mechanically, it operates with the precision of a new assembly, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards. This is an exemplary specimen for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
