    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it in a climate-controlled garage, and stayed on top of every single service. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
