    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its visceral driving dynamics. At its heart lies the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing replacement, addressing critical preventative maintenance. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, tactile engagement, while the M-variable differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This chassis remains structurally rigid and mechanically peerless, free from any parasitic fluid loss or bushing deflection.",
